name: Flying AIR CANADA'S 737 MAX! Vancouver to Calgary
description:
Air Canada's Boeing 737 MAXs finally returned to service earlier this year, after being grounded for nearly two years.

I haven’t flown on the Air Canada MAX since before the grounding, when I flew it in Business from Toronto to Calgary back in August of 2018.

Seeing as I haven’t tried it in Economy yet, I thought this might make for a more interesting late night flight!
